<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>展会</title>
<meta id="viewport" name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<meta name="renderer" content="webkit">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">

<link href="../css/global.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<link href="../css/layout.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<link href="../css/buyer.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<link href="../css/dropkick.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<style type="text/css">
.dk_toggle,
.dk_container{
	height: 28px;
	line-height: 28px;
}
.dk_container{
	border: #ff7c8b solid 1px;
}
.rf-select{
	margin-left: 15px;
}
</style>

<script src="../js/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="../js/jquery.dropkick-min.js"></script>
<script src="../js/expo.public.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">

$(document).ready(function(){
	/*下拉选择框*/
	$('.rf-select').dropkick({autoWidth:true});
});

</script>

<body>
	<div class="M_Header">
		<div class="hd-bg">
			<p class="hd-pink"></p>
		</div>
		<div class="hd-index M_Center">
			<div class="hd-main">
				<ul class="float-center clearfix">
					<li class="hd-m-btn" ><a href="#">展会</a></li>
					<li class="hd-m-btn fixed"><a href="#">社团铺</a></li>
					<li class="hd-m-logo"></li>
					<li class="hd-m-btn" ><a href="#">我的</a></li>
					<li class="hd-m-btn" ><a href="#">同人闲情</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="hd-nav-r">
				<ul class="hd-nav-not">
					<li><a href="#">登录</a></li>
					<li><a href="#">注册</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="M_Center M_Layout M_BTM_175">
		<div class="refund-bg clearfix">
			<div class="refund-step">
				<ul class="clearfix">
					<li class="fixed"><i class="one"></i>买家申请退货退款</li>
					<li><i class="two"></i>卖家处理退货申请</li>
					<li><i class="three"></i>买家退货给卖家</li>
					<li><i class="four"></i>卖家确认收货，退款完成</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="refund-left">
				<div class="refund-fill">
					<p class="rf-s1 clearfix">
						<i>申请服务:</i>
						<select class="rf-select">
							<option value="退货退款">退货退款</option>
							<option value="仅退款">仅退款</option>
						</select>
					</p>
					<p class="rf-p1"><b>*</b>为必填项</p>
					<p class="rf-p2">注：本子，展会门票等不支持退货操作</p>
					<p class="rf-p3"><i>需要退款金额:</i><b>*</b><b>238.00</b>元</p>
					<p class="rf-p3"><i>退款原因:</i><b>*</b><textarea></textarea></p>
					<p class="rf-p3"><i>上传凭证:</i> <input type="file"/></p>
					<p class="rf-p3"><i></i> <input type="file"/></p>
					<p class="rf-btn"> <input type="button" value="提交申请"/> </p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="refund-right">
				<div class="refund-order">
					<p class="ro-p1">退款/退货申请</p>
					<p class="ro-item clearfix">
						<a class="ro-i-img" href="#"><img src="../images/artwork-box-1.jpg"/></a>
						<a class="ri-i-txt" href="#">迪士尼动画长片(疯狂动物城)同人本</a>
					</p>
					<p class="ro-p2"><i>单 价:</i>238.00元*1（数量）</p>
					<p class="ro-p2"><i>套 餐:</i>本子+特典</p>
					<p class="ro-p2"><i>宝贝实付:</i>238.00元</p>
					<p class="ro-p2"><i>运 费:</i>0.00元</p>
					<p class="ro-p2"><i>订单编号:</i><b>150330031545001</b></p>
				</div>
				<div class="refund-shop">
					<p class="ro-p2"><i>卖 家:</i>taiyanhua@163.com</p>
					<a class="ro-call" href="#"><b>联系客服</b></a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>